      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CLIFTON JASPER (3) pinged the lids and led throughout to score last start (30.03) at this track in Grade 5 over 520m. Yet to taste defeat from three runs out of this box. Well placed and will be tough to beat. WEST ON COLE (2) showed good speed off a low draw but weakened and run over late when 5th over 520m at this track in Grade 4/5 company. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Has ability and can atone. SILENT ASSASSIN (8) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind CLIFTON JASPER (30.09) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Expected to feature. JAFFA'S MONELLI (1) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.",
